task_description: Navigate to Apotek Cempaka Putih. Head south down the narrow residential alley and turn left at the T-junction. Continue straight, then turn right onto Jl. Cempaka at the intersection where a blue-domed mosque is visible in the distance. Proceed straight, passing the Griya Yatim & Dhuafa orphanage on the left, to reach the destination on the left.
